Setup and Installation for OCR

### Tesseract OCR
 ** must be installed separately from [Tesseract GitHub Releases page](https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract)
 ** have to ensure that tesseract is in the correct path. ideal: 'C:\Program Files\Tesseract-OCR' to system's Path environment variable

 ### Python Environment Setup
 ** creating the environment: in terminal type
 python -m venv .venv-syllabus

 ** activation step
 (windows)
 .\.venc-syllabus\Scripts\Activate

 (macOS)
source .venv-syllabus/bin/activate

** install dependencies: in terminal type
pip install -r requirements.txt

## running the OCR processor
main script 'ocr_processor.py' desinged to accept any image path as a command-line argument
 **in terminal type: 
(macOS)
python app/ocr/ocr_processor.py <then path to image being tested>